minikube ip --- to get he ip where the application is hosted
minikube start -- to start the minikube 
minikube status -- to check the status of the minikube
kubectl get pods -- to check the running pods 
kubectl get service -- to check the service
kubectl get deployment -- to check the deployed application
kubectl apply -f client-pod.yaml --to apply the pod
kubectl apply -f client-deployment.yaml -- to apply the deployment
kubectl get pods -o wide -- to get more details along with ip address
kubectl describe pods -- to get the more details of the pods
kubectl get deployments -- to check the status of the deployments
